"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-comment-olympics-paris-games-2024-athletics-team-gb-dina-asher-smith-b1172834.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Comment  Get our award-winning daily news email featuring exclusive stories, opinion and expert analysis    I would like to be emailed about offers, event and updates from Evening Standard.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are now just days away from theParisOlympics- the first in Europe since London 2012.\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 519, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999979486347, \"rank\": 2.0511609908625015e-09, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How the world has changed since then.\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be my 10th Games - twice as a competitor and eight times as a sports administrator.\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Often the build-up is challenging - and then the magic starts.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We all fall in love with the Olympics again.\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Track and field athletics is often at the heart of this spectacle.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the British team we are sending to France has some great stars -Keely Hodgkinson,Dina Asher-Smith,Josh Kerr,Molly Caudery,Matt Hudson-Smithand many, many more who can become national heroes in the next few weeks.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 849, \"end\": 856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9964582907302757, \"rank\": 0.003288375897089047, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 880, \"end\": 886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8181924527615821, \"rank\": 0.21777731650004878, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 909, \"end\": 925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 926, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dina Asher-Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9999999965734787, \"rank\": 3.07781673699115e-09, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Caudery\", \"score\": 0.999995872758395, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Molly Caudery\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Caudery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Caudery\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletics is compellingbecause it is the original Olympic sport.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At heart it remains gloriously simple and utterly accessible.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Today you can still turn up at an athletics track and chase your dreams regardless of your background.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The recent Daley Thompson documentary showed how the sport enabled one of our greatest Olympians to do this in the Eighties.\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1300, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daley_Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daley Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daley_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daley_Thompson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That story is repeated day in, day out at athletics clubs around Britain.\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9995342042545367, \"rank\": 0.00046542124998714767, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am proud that kids watching our athletes during the Olympics and then the Paralympics a couple of weeks later will see themselves reflected back    It is also one of the country's most diverse sports with athletes drawn from every kind of community and background.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of the heart-breakingEuro 2024 finalagainst Spain, Labour's new Culture Secretary Lisa Nandy said the England men's team looked, sounded and felt like modern Britain.\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1806, \"end\": 1811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9665118019385818, \"rank\": 0.03459238758270272, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\", \"score\": 0.6920208651401631, \"rank\": 0.40479140123470336, \"text\": \"Labour\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 1826, \"end\": 1843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Secretary_of_State_for_Digital,_Culture,_Media_and_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999974052986556, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Culture Secretary\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Secretary_of_State_for_Digital,_Culture,_Media_and_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Secretary_of_State_for_Digital,_Culture,_Media_and_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1844, \"end\": 1854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Nandy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lisa Nandy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Nandy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Nandy\"}, {\"begin\": 1864, \"end\": 1871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9981033455416948, \"rank\": 0.0017847560822250963, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1920, \"end\": 1927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9995342042545367, \"rank\": 0.00046542124998714767, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At athletics we tell that same inclusive story and I am proud that kids watching our athletes during the Olympics and then the Paralympics a couple of weeks later will see themselves reflected back.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope the performances they see will serve as an inspiration for everyone to get active and get involved in the sport - whether that's joining a club to pursue their hope of winning gold or signing up for a Parkrun.\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2337, \"end\": 2344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parkrun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Parkrun\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parkrun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parkrun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a governing body the past couple of years have been tough.\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2408, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But our finances are now stable and we are turning the corner.\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are making the London Diamond League meeting the biggest and best one-day athletics event in the world.\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And we are looking at how we can bring the World Championships back to London in 2029.\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2650, \"end\": 2656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999993790308618, \"rank\": 5.321266657309667e-07, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The standards at the Paris Olympics are going to be off the chart.\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Records have been tumbling all summer.\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Almost every country in the world sends an athletics team to the Games.\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In many events, just reaching the finals will be an amazing achievement.\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So please get behind our dynamic team in Paris with its great blend of youth and experience.\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 3011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2960, \"end\": 2965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999499778, \"rank\": 4.9893855896616936e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And getready for the magic.\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jack Buckner is the chief executive of UK Athletics and two-time British Olympian  MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool X